snippet.title: El Paso, Elsewhere - XBOX ANNOUNCEMENT TRAILER
snippet.description:
STAKES. GUNS. SLOW-MO. Take a one-way trip into El Paso, Elsewhere: a new, third-person love letter to classic shooters coming to PC and Xbox, Fall 2023. Neo-noir never looked so good.
